column16: Carlos Beltran singles on a ground ball.  Carlos Correa out at 2nd, hit by batted ball, second baseman Brian Dozier unassisted.
Carlos Correa grounds into a force out, second baseman Brian Dozier to shortstop Jorge Polanco.   Jake Marisnick scores.    George Springer to 3rd.    Jose Altuve out at 2nd.    Carlos Correa to 1st.
Jose Altuve singles on a soft ground ball to third baseman Miguel Sano.   Jake Marisnick to 3rd.    George Springer to 2nd.
Josh Reddick pops out to third baseman Miguel Sano on the infield fly rule.
George Springer singles on a line drive to right fielder Max Kepler.   Jake Marisnick to 2nd.
Alex Bregman homers (4) on a fly ball to left center field.   Marwin Gonzalez scores.
Marwin Gonzalez doubles (7) on a ground ball to left fielder Ehire Adrianza.
Mookie Betts grounds into a double play, third baseman Miguel Sano to second baseman Eduardo Escobar to first baseman Kennys Vargas.   Josh Rutledge out at 2nd.
Sandy Leon called out on strikes.
Chris Young homers (2) on a fly ball to left center field.
Mitch Moreland strikes out on a foul tip.
Hanley Ramirez strikes out on a foul tip.
Andrew Benintendi singles on a ground ball to right fielder Robbie Grossman.   Xander Bogaerts to 2nd.
Xander Bogaerts singles on a ground ball to center fielder Max Kepler.
Dustin Pedroia lines out to right fielder Robbie Grossman.
Mookie Betts flies out to right fielder Robbie Grossman.
Sandy Leon grounds out softly, pitcher Drew Rucinski to first baseman Kennys Vargas.
Mitch Moreland doubles (14) on a line drive to left fielder Eddie Rosario.   Hanley Ramirez scores.
Hanley Ramirez singles on a line drive to right fielder Robbie Grossman.   Andrew Benintendi scores.
